#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an3.48"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.48:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.48:0.2"
msgid "5. Cūḷavagga "
msgstr "5. The Lesser Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.48:0.3"
msgid "48. Pabbatarājasutta "
msgstr "48. The King of Mountains "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an3.48:1.1"
msgid "“Himavantaṃ, bhikkhave, pabbatarājaṃ nissāya mahāsālā tīhi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, great sal trees grow in three ways supported by the Himalayas, the king of mountains. "

msgctxt "an3.48:1.2"
msgid "Katamāhi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.48:1.3"
msgid "Sākhāpattapalāsena vaḍḍhanti, tacapapaṭikāya vaḍḍhanti, pheggusārena vaḍḍhanti. "
msgstr "The branches, leaves, and foliage; the bark and shoots; and the softwood and heartwood. "

msgctxt "an3.48:1.4"
msgid "Himavantaṃ, bhikkhave, pabbatarājaṃ nissāya mahāsālā imāhi tīhi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhanti. "
msgstr "Great sal trees grow in these three ways supported by the Himalayas, the king of mountains. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an3.48:2.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, saddhaṃ kulapatiṃ nissāya anto jano tīhi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhati. "
msgstr "In the same way, a family grows in three ways supported by a family head with faith. "

msgctxt "an3.48:2.2"
msgid "Katamāhi tīhi? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "an3.48:2.3"
msgid "Saddhāya vaḍḍhati, sīlena vaḍḍhati, paññāya vaḍḍhati. "
msgstr "Faith, ethics, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an3.48:2.4"
msgid "Saddhaṃ, bhikkhave, kulapatiṃ nissāya anto jano imāhi tīhi vaḍḍhīhi vaḍḍhatīti. "
msgstr "A family grows in these three ways supported by a family head with faith. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an3.48:3.1"
msgid "Yathāpi pabbato selo, "
msgstr "Supported by the mountain crags "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:3.2"
msgid "araññasmiṃ brahāvane; "
msgstr "in the wilds, the formidable forest, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:3.3"
msgid "Taṃ rukkhā upanissāya, "
msgstr "the tree grows "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:3.4"
msgid "vaḍḍhante te vanappatī. "
msgstr "to become lord of the forest. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an3.48:4.1"
msgid "Tatheva sīlasampannaṃ, "
msgstr "So too, when the family head "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:4.2"
msgid "saddhaṃ kulapatiṃ idha; "
msgstr "is ethical and faithful, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:4.3"
msgid "Upanissāya vaḍḍhanti, "
msgstr "supported by them, they grow: "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:4.4"
msgid "puttadārā ca bandhavā; "
msgstr "children, partners, and kin, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:4.5"
msgid "Amaccā ñātisaṅghā ca, "
msgstr "colleagues, relatives, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:4.6"
msgid "ye cassa anujīvino. "
msgstr "and those dependent for their livelihood. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.153, sc5
msgctxt "an3.48:5.1"
msgid "Tyāssa sīlavato sīlaṃ, "
msgstr "Seeing the ethical conduct of the virtuous, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:5.2"
msgid "cāgaṃ sucaritāni ca; "
msgstr "the generosity and good deeds, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:5.3"
msgid "Passamānānukubbanti, "
msgstr "those who see clearly "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: attamatthaṃ → ye bhavanti (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an3.48:5.4"
msgid "attamatthaṃ vicakkhaṇā. "
msgstr "do likewise. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an3.48:6.1"
msgid "Idha dhammaṃ caritvāna, "
msgstr "Having practiced the teaching here, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:6.2"
msgid "maggaṃ sugatigāminaṃ; "
msgstr "the path that goes to a good place, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:6.3"
msgid "Nandino devalokasmiṃ, "
msgstr "they delight in the heavenly realm, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an3.48:6.4"
msgid "modanti kāmakāmino”ti. "
msgstr "enjoying all the pleasures they desire.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.48:6.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
